\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 12\n | RelDate         = December 1992\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-03075-2\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori and the Terrifying Presents\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u306e\u304d\u3087\u3046\u3075\u306e\u30d7\u30ec\u30bc\u30f3\u30c8|\"Kaiketsu Zorori no Ky\u014dfu no Purezento\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 13\n | RelDate         = June 1993\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-03086-8\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori and the Great Riddle Plan\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u306e\u306a\u305e\u306a\u305e\u5927\u3055\u304f\u305b\u3093|\"Kaiketsu Zorori no Nazo Nazo Daisakusen\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 14\n | RelDate         = December 1993\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-03095-0\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori and the Terrifying Soccer\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u306e\u304d\u3087\u3046\u3075\u306e\u30b5\u30c3\u30ab\u30fc|\"Kaiketsu Zorori no Ky\u014dfu no Sakk\u0101\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 15\n | RelDate         = July 1994\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-04400-1\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori Arrested!!\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u3064\u304b\u307e\u308b\uff01\uff01|\"Kaiketsu Zorori Tsukamaru!!\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 16\n | RelDate         = November 1994\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-04623-4\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori and the Mysterious Airplane\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u3068\u306a\u305e\u306e\u3072\u3053\u3046\u304d|\"Kaiketsu Zorori to Nazo no Hik\u014dki\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 17\n | RelDate         = June 1995\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-04801-6\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori and the Great Ghost Plan\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u306e\u304a\u3070\u3051\u5927\u3055\u