i\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 27\n | RelDate         = July 2000\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-06503-7\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori, the Detective Has Appeared\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u306e\u3081\u3044\u305f\u3093\u3066\u3044\u3068\u3046\u3058\u3087\u3046|\"Kaiketsu Zorori no Meitantei T\u014dj\u014d\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 28\n | RelDate         = December 2000\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-06641-6\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori, Certain Death\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u305c\u3063\u305f\u3044\u305c\u3064\u3081\u3044|\"Kaiketsu Zorori Zettai Zetsumei\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 29\n | RelDate         = July 2001\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-06891-5\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori and the Terrifying Carnival\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u306e\u304d\u3087\u3046\u3075\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30cb\u30d0\u30eb|\"Kaiketsu Zorori no Ky\u014dfu no K\u0101nibaru\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 30\n | RelDate         = December 2001\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-07045-1\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori, It's Hot! A Ramen Showdown\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea \u3042\u3064\u3044\u305c\uff01\u30e9\u30fc\u30e1\u30f3\u305f\u3044\u3051\u3064|\"Kaiketsu Zorori Atsui ze! R\u0101men Taiketsu\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 31\n | RelDate         = July 2002\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-07308-7\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori, Heaven and Hell\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be\u30ed\u30ea\u306e\u3066\u3093\u3054\u304f\u3068\u3058\u3054\u304f|\"Kaiketsu Zorori no Tengoku to Jigoku\"}}\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 32\n | RelDate         = December 2002\n | ISBN            = 978-4-591-07446-6\n | Title           = {{nihongo|\"Kaiketsu Zorori, a Trip to Hell\"|\u304b\u3044\u3051\u3064\u30be